title: Niall Annett
text:
Niall Annett (born 7 May 1991) is a professional <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player for <a href="Worcester%20Warriors">Worcester Warriors</a>, having previously played for <a href="Ulster%20Rugby">Ulster Rugby</a>. His favoured position is hooker.
In the 2011 junior Rugby Championships, Annett captained the Ireland U20 team.
In 2014, he was called up to the <a href="Barbarian%20F.C.">Barbarians</a> squad to play against <a href="Leicester%20Tigers">Leicester Tigers</a>.
